## v1.0.0 (2026-05-13)

**Initial version.** Documented the hostile-`$HOME` 8-shape matrix used to
confirm modular/modular#6412 (`getAcceleratorArchOrEmpty()` `std::filesystem::status`
uncaught `filesystem_error`) was fixed in `mojo==1.0.0b2.dev2026050805` before
peeling back downstream Dockerfile chmod / entrypoint mkdir workarounds.
Verification level: verified-local (executed inside `podman compose exec -T
projectodyssey-dev`; true cross-UID NOT testable in rootless podman).
